    "Html": "<p>Hi<br><br>I am trying to create a wpf datagrid with multiple groups as shown in the image below.<br><br><img src=\"http://i629.photobucket.com/albums/uu13/cheapsaket/grouping.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n<p>Currently I have been able to set one grouping only for example Country. But I want to be able to group at a second level like State atleast.<br><br>Is&nbsp;the WPF Datagrid capable of such grouping?</p>",
